{"tid":1636594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（幫推上熱門）可唔可以推返啲正經野","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:42:08.000Z","uid":186874,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"19953ad057885f8395ff12c8bac21c3cb6a3eb6a","tid":1636594,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:47:58.000Z","msg":"eg<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣:</span></span><br />\n解釋點解裝修<br />\n有咩行動<br />\n共狗惡行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動：</span></span><br />\n整理商場<br />\n三罷<br />\n全民口罩<br />\n提款<br />\n罷買<br />\n罷tvb冇咗？<br />\n簽名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰略：</span></span><br />\n點打仗 <br />\n點文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提議：</span></span><br />\n理髮/關節技 代替 制暴<br />\n點用字眼（手捉, 武器）<br />\n裝飾/蟲/1823/openrice comment/攞飛/淨坐 代替 裝修<br />\n落街派口罩/文宣<br />\n（好多時可以智取btw,智勇雙全）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">突發：</span></span><br />\n邊度有狗<br />\n唔好去邊<br />\n邊度要人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">btw:</span></span><br />\n未fc/on9 咪再推 <br />\n（已經有2個fake news 冇source上咗熱門）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">6月嗰時全版熱門都係有用野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推正經野啦 鍵盤戰士</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5b0d75e55d8b5f7a46ecb945db0cb5006a9e208e","tid":1636594,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:48:30.000Z","msg":"help"},{"pid":"975e11325f05742d21ea72f01cbc71c0fb97285a","tid":1636594,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"反五毛"},{"pid":"a4f6fcec926381e4c7c9505147beeaf3e6fa1099","tid":1636594,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0